Name: Balm Lily Flower
Description:
A medicinal flower that soothes most minor maladies.

It is exceptionally fragrant.

Name: Reed Fiber
Description: A ball of raw cellulose used in the production of Clothing and textiles.

Name: Lumber
Description: Wood harvested from an Arbor Tree.

Name: Warm Sweater
Description: Protects the wearer from Cold by increasing insulation.

Name: Cool Vest
Description: Protects the wearer from Heat by decreasing insulation.

Name: Snazzy Suit
Description: Increases Decor in a small area effect around the wearer.

Name: Egg Shell
Description: Can be crushed to produce Lime.

Name: Pokeshell Molt
Description: Can be crushed to produce Lime.

Name: Pokeshell Molt
Description: Can be crushed to produce Lime.

Name: Table Salt
Description: A seasoning that Duplicants can add to their Food to boost Morale. Duplicants will automatically use Table Salt while sitting at a Mess Table during mealtime. Only the finest grains are chosen.

Name: Atmo Suit
Description: Supplies Duplicants with Oxygen in toxic and low breathability environments.

Name: Jet Suit
Description:
Supplies Duplicants with Oxygen in toxic and low breathability environments.

Allows Duplicant flight.

Name: Data Bank
Description: Raw data that can be processed into Interstellar Research points.

Name: Vacillator Recharge
Description: Replenishes one charge to a depleted Neural Vacillator.

Name: Rot Pile
Description:
An inedible glop of former foodstuff.

Rot Piles break down into Polluted Dirt over time.
